nodes.text: Good morning. I just received word from Org1 that, according to CDC guidelines, I don qualify for a booster shot at this time in spite of the fact that i In the XX+ age category. I continue to monitor   The situation. If you have any thoughts, comments or opinions please feel free to get back to me. I continue on my daily regimen of abiraterone acetate and prednisone and I feel fine; i Sleeping well, eating well and exercising. Hard to shed a few pounds (around 190) and I guess my glucose remains elevated (7.5) because of the prednisone, according to my primary.
